name: Skye (Fortnite)
description:
Check out my Twitter where I post daily and you can check my commission status there.
I have a Patreon where I post loads of NSFW work every month and on my feed!

Update on the 2.0:

Kotosmix -> Trained on Pseudo model

512x512 -> 640x640 resolution

Here's a couple tips, and if you have any questions feel free to ask:

  • Upscaling even at 1.25x +0.3 denoising works wonders

  • Euler A will make slight variations at every step. If you're unhappy with slight problems, like the fingers, try +1 steps.

  • LoRA Strength at 0.5-1 generates a wide array of options

  • specify the clothing color

  • Use my images to get an idea on how I'm prompting :^ )
